sellerCard.oneLiner: Expert Full Stack Developer ! From Concept to Deployment
sellerCard.description: Hello! I'm a Full Stack Developer with over 7 years of experience in crafting seamless, efficient, and scalable web and mobile applications. I specialize in both front-end and back-end technologies and have a deep understanding of building responsive, user-centric applications from scratch to deployment. Whether you're looking to build a modern website, a complex web app, or mobile solutions, I can bring your ideas to life with clean, maintainable code and cutting-edge tech.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What requirements I have to provide?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You have to provide clear requirements including main functionalities for the website. Provide Wireframe or sketch if you can.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What will be the final costing?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: It depends on the complexity of the website. We can have a detail conversation regarding this matter depending on your budget and requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why do i need to reach you before placing an order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: To complete all the requirements and to assure that I can fulfill your all desire expectation and requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide any support after order completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, My main goal is to develop your business, not just the website. I will surely give you full support even after completion of order.

Grateful to have had his expertise and mindset driving this part of the journey.

His open lines of communication and iterative approach made a big difference in refining along the way and setting things up for continued development.
